---
import Layout from '../../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout title='Plasterers & Painters in Binfield | Hancock' description='Plastering and painting in Binfield. Fixed-price quotes from City & Guilds certified contractors covering Binfield and the surrounding area.' activePage='areas'>
<section style="position:relative;height:340px;display:flex;align-items:flex-end;">
  <div style="position:absolute;top:0;left:0;right:0;bottom:0;background-image:url('/uploads/Hancock-plastering-and-painting%20(3).webp');background-size:cover;background-position:center 40%;"></div>
  <div style="position:absolute;top:0;left:0;right:0;bottom:0;background:linear-gradient(to top,rgba(15,23,42,0.9) 0%,rgba(15,23,42,0.45) 60%,rgba(15,23,42,0.15) 100%);"></div>
  <div style="position:relative;z-index:1;max-width:1280px;margin:0 auto;padding:0 24px 48px;width:100%;box-sizing:border-box;">
    <p style="font-family:'Inter',sans-serif;font-size:12px;color:rgba(255,255,255,0.55);margin:0 0 12px;"><a href="/" style="color:rgba(255,255,255,0.55);text-decoration:none;">Home</a> / <a href="/areas" style="color:rgba(255,255,255,0.55);text-decoration:none;">Areas</a> / Binfield</p>
    <h1 style="font-family:'Lexend',sans-serif;font-size:clamp(30px,5vw,52px);font-weight:700;color:#ffffff;margin:0 0 10px;letter-spacing:-0.04em;line-height:1.05;">Plasterer in Binfield</h1>
    <p style="font-family:'Inter',sans-serif;font-size:16px;color:rgba(255,255,255,0.75);margin:0;">RG42 · Plastering &amp; decorating for Binfield's village and modern residential.</p>
  </div>
</section>
<section style="padding:56px 24px;background:#ffffff;border-bottom:1px solid #E2E8F0;">
  <div style="max-width:1280px;margin:0 auto;">
    <p style="font-family:'Inter',sans-serif;font-size:12px;font-weight:600;color:#11ADE2;letter-spacing:0.1em;text-transform:uppercase;margin:0 0 12px;">About Binfield</p>
    <h2 style="font-family:'Lexend',sans-serif;font-size:clamp(20px,3vw,30px);font-weight:600;color:#0F172A;margin:0 0 18px;letter-spacing:-0.03em;line-height:1.2;">A village that has grown significantly — a traditional core surrounded by substantial 1990s–2010s residential development.</h2>
    <p style="font-family:'Inter',sans-serif;font-size:15px;color:#334155;line-height:1.75;margin:0 0 14px;">Binfield village has expanded considerably in recent decades with large residential developments on its edges. The newer housing stock is modern cavity wall construction — skimming, interior painting, and plastering after extension work are the typical domestic jobs. The older village core has period properties with more traditional construction.</p>
  </div>
</section>
<section style="padding:56px 24px;background:#F8FAFC;border-bottom:1px solid #E2E8F0;">
  <div style="max-width:1280px;margin:0 auto;">
    <p style="font-family:'Inter',sans-serif;font-size:12px;font-weight:600;color:#11ADE2;letter-spacing:0.1em;text-transform:uppercase;margin:0 0 12px;">Common problems</p>
    <h2 style="font-family:'Lexend',sans-serif;font-size:clamp(20px,3vw,28px);font-weight:600;color:#0F172A;margin:0 0 28px;letter-spacing:-0.03em;">What goes wrong in Binfield's housing stock.</h2>
    <div style="display:grid;grid-template-columns:repeat(auto-fit,minmax(240px,1fr));gap:20px;">
      <div style="background:#ffffff;border:1px solid #E2E8F0;border-radius:8px;padding:24px;"><h3 style="font-family:'Lexend',sans-serif;font-size:16px;font-weight:600;color:#0F172A;margin:0 0 8px;">New-build extension cracking</h3><p style="font-family:'Inter',sans-serif;font-size:14px;color:#334155;line-height:1.65;margin:0;">The modern estate housing is cavity-built; new extensions and the junctions between phases settle and crack as they dry and move, needing cutting back and re-skimming.</p></div>
      <div style="background:#ffffff;border:1px solid #E2E8F0;border-radius:8px;padding:24px;"><h3 style="font-family:'Lexend',sans-serif;font-size:16px;font-weight:600;color:#0F172A;margin:0 0 8px;">Refit re-skims</h3><p style="font-family:'Inter',sans-serif;font-size:14px;color:#334155;line-height:1.65;margin:0;">Kitchen and bathroom renovations on the newer homes leave walls that need a full re-skim to give a flat, paint-ready surface.</p></div>
      <div style="background:#ffffff;border:1px solid #E2E8F0;border-radius:8px;padding:24px;"><h3 style="font-family:'Lexend',sans-serif;font-size:16px;font-weight:600;color:#0F172A;margin:0 0 8px;">Period repair in the old core</h3><p style="font-family:'Inter',sans-serif;font-size:14px;color:#334155;line-height:1.65;margin:0;">The older village centre has traditional-construction properties with solid walls needing sympathetic, breathable repair.</p></div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
<section style="padding:56px 24px;background:#ffffff;border-bottom:1px solid #E2E8F0;">
  <div style="max-width:1280px;margin:0 auto;">
    <div style="display:flex;gap:64px;flex-wrap:wrap;margin-bottom:48px;">
      <div style="flex:1;min-width:300px;">
        <p style="font-family:'Inter',sans-serif;font-size:12px;font-weight:600;color:#11ADE2;letter-spacing:0.1em;text-transform:uppercase;margin:0 0 12px;">Neighbourhoods we work in</p>
        <h2 style="font-family:'Lexend',sans-serif;font-size:clamp(20px,3vw,28px);font-weight:600;color:#0F172A;margin:0 0 18px;letter-spacing:-0.03em;line-height:1.2;">A village expanded by modern development.</h2>
        <p style="font-family:'Inter',sans-serif;font-size:15px;color:#334155;line-height:1.75;margin:0 0 14px;">Binfield has grown considerably over recent decades, with large residential developments — including the substantial <strong>Blue Mountain and Amen Corner</strong> schemes — wrapping around a traditional village core. The newer stock is modern cavity-wall construction; the older centre around the church and the high street retains period properties.</p>
        <p style="font-family:'Inter',sans-serif;font-size:15px;color:#334155;line-height:1.75;margin:0;">It's a family-home market with strong demand for skimming, extension plastering, and decorating on the newer homes.</p>
      </div>
      <div style="flex:1;min-width:300px;">
        <p style="font-family:'Inter',sans-serif;font-size:12px;font-weight:600;color:#11ADE2;letter-spacing:0.1em;text-transform:uppercase;margin:0 0 12px;">What homeowners ask for</p>
        <h2 style="font-family:'Lexend',sans-serif;font-size:clamp(20px,3vw,28px);font-weight:600;color:#0F172A;margin:0 0 18px;letter-spacing:-0.03em;line-height:1.2;">Skimming, painting, and plastering.</h2>
        <p style="font-family:'Inter',sans-serif;font-size:15px;color:#334155;line-height:1.75;margin:0 0 14px;">The newer homes drive re-skims after refits, plastering out extensions, and interior and exterior painting. The village core brings occasional period repair. Exterior work is scheduled for the drier months.</p>
        <p style="font-family:'Inter',sans-serif;font-size:15px;color:#334155;line-height:1.75;margin:0;">Mid-market budgets, done once and done well, fixed price up front.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
    <p style="font-family:'Inter',sans-serif;font-size:12px;font-weight:600;color:#11ADE2;letter-spacing:0.1em;text-transform:uppercase;margin:0 0 24px;">Working in Binfield</p>
    <div style="display:grid;grid-template-columns:repeat(auto-fit,minmax(220px,1fr));gap:20px;">
      <div><h3 style="font-family:'Lexend',sans-serif;font-size:15px;font-weight:600;color:#0F172A;margin:0 0 8px;">~40 minutes from base</h3><p style="font-family:'Inter',sans-serif;font-size:14px;color:#334155;line-height:1.65;margin:0;">At the south-western edge of the corridor, reached via the M25 and M4. Covered on planned runs with Bracknell and Ascot.</p></div>
      <div><h3 style="font-family:'Lexend',sans-serif;font-size:15px;font-weight:600;color:#0F172A;margin:0 0 8px;">New-build ready</h3><p style="font-family:'Inter',sans-serif;font-size:14px;color:#334155;line-height:1.65;margin:0;">We handle the settlement and junction cracking that comes with newer cavity-built homes and extensions properly.</p></div>
      <div><h3 style="font-family:'Lexend',sans-serif;font-size:15px;font-weight:600;color:#0F172A;margin:0 0 8px;">Easy access</h3><p style="font-family:'Inter',sans-serif;font-size:14px;color:#334155;line-height:1.65;margin:0;">Modern estate streets and driveways give straightforward room for the van and materials on any job size.</p></div>
      <div><h3 style="font-family:'Lexend',sans-serif;font-size:15px;font-weight:600;color:#0F172A;margin:0 0 8px;">Clean, tidy, insured</h3><p style="font-family:'Inter',sans-serif;font-size:14px;color:#334155;line-height:1.65;margin:0;">Surfaces protected, site left tidy daily. Fully insured, City &amp; Guilds qualified, no subcontractors.</p></div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
<section style="padding:0;">
  <div style="position:relative;height:clamp(300px,42vw,440px);">
    <div style="position:absolute;inset:0;background-image:url('/uploads/Hancock-plastering-and-painting%20(2).webp');background-size:cover;background-position:center;"></div>
    <div style="position:absolute;inset:0;background:linear-gradient(to top,rgba(15,23,42,0.78) 0%,rgba(15,23,42,0.18) 55%,rgba(15,23,42,0) 100%);"></div>
    <div style="position:relative;max-width:1280px;margin:0 auto;height:100%;display:flex;align-items:flex-end;padding:0 24px 40px;box-sizing:border-box;">
      <p style="font-family:'Lexend',sans-serif;font-size:clamp(18px,2.4vw,26px);font-weight:600;color:#ffffff;max-width:600px;margin:0;letter-spacing:-0.02em;line-height:1.3;">Skimmed flat and consistent — the foundation of a finish that lasts.</p>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
